Class Employee

  • java.lang.Object
    • functionality.Person
      • functionality.Employee
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Employee
extends Person
implements java.io.Serializable
    Employee is an extension of the Person class.This class extends the Person with functionality to store preferences of work and the training of the employee
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Kenneth Jensen, Florin Bordei, Teakosheen Joulak, Jimmi Børgesen
